title: Captain Caitlyn :D

embed.description: Captain Caitlyn photo: League of Legends Skin Concept This photo was uploaded by jesseboy101

body: Her Q shoots harpoons, ult is a torpedo and the mine is her snare. hope you like it :3 {{champion:51}}

replies.body: I think she'd look better with a proper navy-style skirt and blouse, even if you kept it in the dress whites style. Beyond that, it's a nice idea.
i could also see this on jinx.. id swap the harpoon for her ult and idk about her q then.. because jinx's ult is more of a massive bomb.. i like the idea and pic tho
